text: Akhlystino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhmetovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 183 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Kushnarenkovo, 11 km from Akhmetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Akhlystino, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
